CatDescriptText: The members of the Caprells were classmates from Gladstone High School in Hazelwood.  The band played extensively in Pittsburgh and toured the Northeast.
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of The Caprells, including David "Skeetz" Peters, Robert D. Jones, Douglas J. Milner, and Louis T. Alexander, posed in diagonal formation with two electric guitars, electric bass, drum sticks in interior with light colored walls and curtains on the right
